summary: a display for all ring types, necklaces, and such from different mods for player homes.
descriptionHtml: this mod will be made to display rings, amulets, and such from many mods to have a display case as it were for those people who wish to BUY a display case from a vendor and place them sort of like the drop down mannequins mod which is similar to this mod but is nothing like it except in appearance. what this mod will incorporate will be a small, medium, and large size display board for either holds, factions, or such for the players to display in there homes.
author: me and others
